		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Your touch can heal wounds.</em></p><p><strong>Bonus Action</strong> - 1 Creature (Touch) - Magical</p><p>You have a pool of healing power that replenishes when you take a long rest. With that pool, you can restore a total number of hit points equal to your paladin level x 5.</p><p>As an action, you can touch a creature and draw power from the pool to restore a number of hit points to that creature, up to the maximum amount remaining in your pool.</p><p>This feature has no effect on &amp;reference[construct].</p>",
